rComments: Very passionate about her subject. Teaches everything clearly, not many homeworks. Very helpful. Mid semester exam was a piece of cake, but final exam was extraordinarily tough. However, marks were increased appropriately at the end of the semester. As I said, very considerate and helpful professor with a lot of knowledge about her subject

A great professor.  Expects you to work hard but grades fairly and if you take her suggestions into account you will do well.  She is very knowledgable on spacecraft mission planning and her passion shows in all of the classes she teaches.
